      "name": "Monte Carlo UQ Coverage Validation",
      "description": "Monte Carlo propagation of inlet velocity, viscosity, and power-law haemolysis model coefficients through the CFD solver yielded 95th-percentile prediction intervals. Interval coverage against the registry observations was 91%, exceeding the 90% nominal coverage target.",
